# Models Directory

Place AI model weights here:

- `silero_vad.onnx` – Silero VAD model (download from [GitHub](https://github.com/snakers4/silero-vad))
- `sensevoice-small-q8.ggml` – SenseVoice quantised model (optional, for local inference)

These files are git-ignored due to their size. Use `git-lfs` or download separately.
